## 📌 Conclusion

The Number Plate Detection Without Helmet project demonstrates the practical use of computer vision and deep learning for traffic surveillance. By automatically detecting riders without helmets and identifying their vehicle number plates, the system helps improve road safety, supports traffic law enforcement, and reduces manual monitoring efforts.

